

**Matsh g Jesus hema ep doaj mihshmda tash ch ed **

1 Sh hema d uhgchu ch d Palasi ch hebai hab juh g geꞌe gegosig ha‑mihshmda tash ed k ash ab i wai g Jesus. Kutsh am jiwia. 2 Sh eda an hema haꞌichug g cheoj ch mahniko nash pi g kakhioj ch nohnhoij ge totskoni. Kumsh an si s‑nenꞌoid g Jesus mas wo doaj nash pi ab haꞌichu s‑abchudamk. 

3 Sh hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui hegam chehanig ha mashchamdam ch Palasi, “Shahchu am ahgch hab elid mo pi t‑hiwgid g t‑chehanig machs wo ha doaj t‑mihshmda tash ed?” 

4 Sh pi hedai has shaꞌi kaij. 

Tsh g Jesus ab hahawa i wai ihda oꞌodham k doajid k am hahawa dagito. Kutsh gam hu hih. 

5 Sh hab hahawa kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Neh, namt hig pi woho ab ha hekaj wo i wuhshad g e‑alidag o chum hems g e‑woiwisga matp am wo sha gei wawhia ch ed, chum as d wo em‑mihshmda tashk?” 

6 Kush pi hedai e nako mas has wo chei. 

**Mamtsh pi wo tatchua mamtsh wo wehpegat am geꞌe gegosig am **

7 Kutsh haꞌi hegam ha‑waida gan hu si wehpeg s‑apko dadhaiwua. Kush am ha neid g Jesus ch hab kaij, 8 “Pi g am hu si s‑apko wo dadhaiwua mamt hekid am wo hihi gegosig wui. Tp hems am hema wo jiwia mat am baꞌich d wo i s‑has haꞌichuk. 9 Kut am haha wabsh wo jiwia hegai mat ab i em‑wai k hab wo em‑ah mamt wo hiwigi hegai s‑has haꞌichu abai mamt ab chum dahiwua. Kumt wo si e el namt pi hahawa ga hu wabsh si ha oidk wo dahiwua. 

10 “Baꞌich at wo i s‑apꞌek mamt ga hu wabsh mehk wo dahiwua. Kut g kihkam ab wo i him k hab wo em‑ah, ‘Ni‑nawoj, oi g i hihm k ia hu s‑apko ni‑miabidch i dahiwua.’ Neh, t id ab wo em‑mah g si has elida am ha tahgio hegam haꞌi ha‑waida. 

11 “Mt wo pi haꞌichuch hegai mat hedai wo chum si e haꞌichuch k ab wo si haꞌichuch hegai mat wo pi e haꞌichuch.” 

12 Sh hab hahawa ep kaij g Jesus ab wui hegai mat ab i wai, “Pi g hegam ab waꞌi ha waid e‑naipijju o g e‑wepnag o g e‑hajuni o g s‑kakais e‑hugid an kihkam mapt hekid hab wo juh g gegosig. Ab at epai wo i m‑wai idam. Kupt hab masma ab wo bei g e‑namkidadag heg hekaj mapt id hab juh. 13 Ab g i ha waid g shoꞌigkam ch mamaniko ch pi hihimidkam ch pi neneadam mapt hekid hab wo juh g gegosig. 14 Pi at wo e nako idam mat wo uhpam m‑namkid. T g Jiosh ab wo m‑mah g s‑kehg m‑mahkigdag mat hekid am wo i ha wuwhas g s‑apꞌekam hemajkam ab muhkig amjed.” 

**Haꞌichu wepogida ahga ab amjed g geꞌe gegosig **

*An g neid g Matthew 22:1-10 *

15 Sh am hema daha g oꞌodham ch kah ihda. Tsh am i haꞌasa neo g Jesus. Sh id ab wui hab kaij, “Ttki wo si s‑hehgigkad, am i wahpk Jiosh kihdag ed, heg wa wepo matt am wo dadhaiwua geꞌe gegosig ch ed.” 

16 Sh hab kaij g Jesus, “Heuꞌu, mamtp woho am wo i wahp. Id o wepo masma matp hems hema hab juh g geꞌe gegosig k muꞌi ab ha waid g hemajkam. 17 T am i e ai. Kut am hema cheha g e‑pionag. T heg am him k ha‑ahgi mo wehs haꞌichu e nahtokch. 

18 “K wabshaba idam am ahgid mat pi wo e nako mat am wo hihi. 

“Neh, tp hems hema am wo ahgi, ‘Ha ant nolawt g oidag k heg s‑neidamk ch hekaj pi am hu wo hih.’ 

19 “Kutp hems hema am wo ahgi, ‘Wehst‑mahm woiwis ant am ha nolawt k hegam s‑ha aꞌappemimk.’ 

20 “Kutp hems hema am wo ahgi, ‘Ha ant hohnt k hekaj pi am hu wo hih.’ 

21 “Neh, t am hahawa uhpam hih ihda ha‑pionag k am ahgi g e‑ahmo. T g ahmoj wabsh woho i bagat k hab kaij ab e‑pionag wui, ‘S‑hohtam g am hihm kahya ch ed ch wohg ch ed k ab wo i ha ui g shoꞌigkam ch mamaniko ch pi neneadam ch pi hihimidkam.’ 

22 “Kut wa woho hab juh k am hahawa jiwia k hab kaij, ‘Bant juh g m‑chehanig. K wabshaba am wabsh kia wiꞌis g kih.’ 

23 “K hab ep kaij g ahmoj, ‘Am g i wuhshani k an mehk hihm chuꞌuchum wopog oidch an shaꞌi ch ed k hab wo ha juh mat ab wo i hihi mat wo shuhd g ni‑kih. 24 Pi at ab hu i hihi hegam mo d chum si ni‑waida. Kunt pi hema wo shaꞌi hiwigi mas wabsh wo i jeh g ni‑gegosig.’ ” 

**Mattsh haschu wo nako nach pi ab si tatchua g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 10:37-38 *

25 Sh am hu hebai hihim hegam Jesus. Sh muꞌi hemajkam am ha wehm hihim. 

Tsh ab i ha nei g Jesus k hab kaij ab ha wui, 26 “Pi am ab hu shaꞌi ni‑tatchua mamtp pi baꞌich ab wo i ni‑tatchua mam hi g e‑jehj ch e‑wepnag ch e‑wehm kihkam ch e‑aꞌaliga. 27 Hemho wa amt gam hu wo dagito g hejel hab e‑elida k ahni hab ni‑elida hab wo junihid ch ni‑wehhejed wo e shoꞌigchudad. Id at heg wo wa wepok mam ab mohto g kots ch ab ab wo e muhkid. 

28 “Neh, nat hig pi am hu wo i aꞌamich hegai matp hedai am hema geꞌe wo kiht mas am hi wa ahim lialiga mat wo nahto g e‑kihta? 29 Mt wo ashad matp am hab wabsh wo juh g shondaj k pi wo e nako mas am hu wo i nahto g e‑kihta. 30 Kut hab wo e chechꞌed, ‘Ihda oꞌodham at am chum hema i kei g kih k wabshaba pi e nako mat wo nahto.’ Pegih, mt ahpim hab wa masma wo i aꞌamich mams wo e nakog k ab wo ni‑hiwgad. 

31 “Neh, matp hems hema g kownal wo s‑cheggiam g e‑obga k eda al wehst‑mahm mihl \(10,000\) wo shondaligak. T g obgaj gokko wehst‑mahm mihl \(20,000\) wo shondaligak ch ab him. T hegai kownal am wo i chum aꞌamich mas hu hi wo wa e nako mat wo cheggia. 32 Tp hab wo mahsk matki pi wo e nako, t hemho wa am wo haꞌi ha cheha mat ab wo nam hegai hema kownal mat ga hu wabsh kia mehk wo himad k wo s‑mai mas heꞌekia wo i namkid. T pi wo cheggia. 33 Neh, bo chuꞌig. Kumt ahpim pi wo e nako mamt ab wo ni‑hiwgad, heg hi wa mamt wehs haꞌichu wo dagito am ni‑wehhejed.” 

**Mattsh onkaj haꞌichu wehhejed wo s‑kehgajk **

*An g neid g Matthew 5:13; Mark 9:50 *

34 Sh hab ep kaij, “Mt haꞌichu wehhejed wo chum s‑kehgajk hab masma mo g on. 35 Heg at gam hu wabsh wo s‑e ohhod mat wo sha kahko. Kumt wo s‑e nenꞌoidad namt pi wabsh wo s‑e ohhod mamtp pi haꞌichu wehhejed wo s‑kehgajk. Ab g wo i aꞌamichud ahpim mam kah ihda.” 

